{"id": "pos040", "name": "Audio_Vicky_702_11_14", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_04"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "Ha... ha! Excuse me!\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Pedestrian"], "content": "Waahhh!\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "Stop! NEKO! PAFF! Stop right there!\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Pedestrian"], "content": "Is that... NEKO and PAFF?\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Pedestrian"], "content": "It really is them!\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Pedestrian"], "content": "Quick, take a picture!\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "image", "attrs": ["nos2606"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "Oh god, oh no! This is bad! This is really, really bad!\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Signal Switches]</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "Waah!\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Fall_over", "Falls down"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Sis Vicky!\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "Don't worry about me! Keep chasing!\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "I can't do that!\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "Damnit! Shouldn't have worn heels...\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Sis Vicky, you twisted your ankle... Can you walk?\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "Yeah, I can... Oww! That hurt...\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "... It looks swollen. You need to get it treated as soon as possible. Here, I'll carry you.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "...... (Offers hand)\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Hnngh... Ha!\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "Footsteps"], "content": ""}, {"id": 22, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»» Fast Forward»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "......\n... Why didn't you keep chasing them!? You dumba**! I'm going to deduct your salary!\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Ow, that hurt... I'm not going to catch them at that distance. There were many pedestrians between us too.\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "You slowed down on purpose, didn't you? When she kept turning around to look at you.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "What you said back at Daniel's place... Those were all true, weren't they?\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "As a professional journalist, I can clearly tell that you're already investigating this story from a completely personal angle. I'm certain that there's still a lot more you know regarding this case, many of which I'm totally unaware of, right?\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "... Guess I can't hide it from sis Vicky anymore... Sorry for not telling you. I was afraid that if I do, you would definitely treat it like exclusive news and write tons of reports on it. I didn't want that to happen...\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "Sighs... By now, that so-called exclusive news is already gone with the wind... Take a look. It's all over iM now, that little chase scene we had back there.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Woah...\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "In terms of this news report, it's my utter defeat. I was totally out of the loop throughout all this. Tell me everything you know, will you?\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "Rest assured. Judging by how you look at her... she is currently in some kind of danger, right? If this news report involves the safety of a person's life, I will back out. I still uphold some basic business ethics, after all.\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Can you promise...?\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "I, Vicky Russell, is exceptional at putting out questions, confutations, speculations and discussions. However, that does not include prevarications. The one thing I loathe the most in life is knowing the truth yet telling a lie on purpose. This is also the reason why I was able to survive in this industry for such a long time.\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Haha... Now that I think about it, it is true. Sis Vicky tends to just cut through all the crap and get straight to the point.\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "Besides, the determination you showed back there, that will to catch up to her no matter what... It reminds me a little of what I used to be... \n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Eh?\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "Don't mind me. All in all, setting aside my role as a journalist, I really want to know the story between you and her.\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "... I... I grew up in Node 03, together with a girl named \"Kaori\"...\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_04"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "はぁ……っ！はぁ…っ！通して！\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["通行人"], "content": "うわ！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "待ちなさい！NEKO！PAFF！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["通行人"], "content": "あれってNEKOとPAFFなの！？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["通行人"], "content": "本当だ！\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["通行人"], "content": "早く撮って！\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "image", "attrs": ["nos2606"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "うわわわ！やばいよ～\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→シグナル切り替え]</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "わっ！\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Fall_over", "転ぶ"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Vickyさん！\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "私のことはいいから！行って！\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "そんなことできませんよ！\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "もう！ハイヒールなんて履いてくるんじゃなかったわ……\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Vickyさん、足を捻ったみたいですね……\n歩けますか？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "大丈夫よ……うわ！イタタタ……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……腫れそうですね。\n冷やさないと。行きますよ。\n僕がおぶります。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "……（手を伸ばす）\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "よいしょ……！\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "足音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 22, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "………\n……なんで私のことを放っておいて追わないのよ！\nもう！給料引くからね！\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "イタタタ……\nあの距離じゃ、追いつきませんよ。\n人もたくさんいたし……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "あんたわざと足を緩めたでしょ。\nあの子があなたを見てるとき。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "あんたがDanielの家で言っていたこと……事実よね？\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "私はプロの記者よ。\nそれくらい分かるわ。\nあんたは完全に私的観点でこの事件を追ってる。\n私の知らないこともたくさん知ってるんでしょ。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……Vickyさんには隠し事はできませんね。\nすみません。\nでも、僕が話してしまえば、必ず独占ニュースとして大々的に報道されてしまうでしょう？\nそれは嫌なんです……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "はぁ……ぶっちゃけ、もう独占ニュースとかどうでもいいのよ。\n見て。さっきの鬼ごっこがもうiMで広まってる。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "わぁ……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "今回の事件については、私の完敗よ。\nだって私は完全に蚊帳の外の人間だもの。\nあなたの知ってることを話してちょうだい。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "大丈夫よ。\nあなたの彼女を見る目……\n彼女は何らかの危険に巻き込まれてるんでしょう？\nこのニュースが人命にかかわるのなら、私は手を引くわ。\nそれくらいのモラル持ち合わせてるわよ。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "本当ですか……？\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "この私Vicky Russellが最も得意とするのは、疑問、反論、推理、議論よ。\nそこに偽物の情報は含まれていないことが前提でね。\n真相を知っていながら、嘘をつくのは嫌いよ。\nこれが、私がこの業界で生き残っている理由でもあるわ。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "はは……そうですね。\nVickyさんはまっすぐな人だから。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "それに、あんたの脇目も振らずに彼女を追いかける様が、ちょっと昔を思い出させてね……\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "え？\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "なんでもないわ。\nとにかく、記者ということは忘れて、あなたたちの物語が聞きたいの。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……僕は……Node03で育ちました……\n「薫（カオリ）」という女の子と一緒に……\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_04"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "哈……哈！借過！\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["路人"], "content": "哇！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "別跑！NEKO！PAFF！站住！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["路人"], "content": "那是 NEKO 跟 PAFF 嗎！？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["路人"], "content": "真的是她們！\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["路人"], "content": "快點拍呀！\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "image", "attrs": ["nos2606"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "哇哇哇！這下糟了！\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "哇！\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Fall_over", "摔倒"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Vicky 姐！\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "別管我！繼續追！\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "那怎麼行！？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "可惡！不該穿高跟鞋的……\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Vicky 姐，妳的腳扭傷了……可以走嗎？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "可以啦……唔啊！好痛……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……好像快腫起來了，要快點包紮才行，來吧，我揹妳。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "……（伸手）\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "嘿咻……！\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 22, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "……。\n……你為什麼不繼續追啊！？可惡！我要扣你薪水！\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "好痛痛痛……那種距離追不到了，中間都是路人。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "你故意放慢速度了吧？在她一直回頭看你的時候。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "你在 Daniel 家說的那些……是真的吧？\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "身為一個專業記者，我看得出來，你已經完全是用自己的角度在追查這件事了。你肯定還知道很多我不知道的事吧？\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……瞞不過 Vicky 姐了啊。對不起……因為說出來的話，這件事情一定會被當成獨家新聞大肆報導，我不希望變成那樣……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "唉……事到如今已經無所謂什麼獨家新聞了……你看，iM 上馬上就傳開了，我們剛剛的追逐戲碼。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "哇……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "我在這條新聞已經可以說是完敗了啊……根本完全是狀況外。把你知道的跟我說吧。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "放心吧，瞧你看她的眼神……她現在處於某種危險中吧？如果這條新聞會牽涉到某人的生命安全，我會收手，這點商業道德我還是有的。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "妳保證嗎……？\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "我 Vicky Russell 最擅長的就是疑論、反論、推論和討論，但可不包括偽論。明明知道真相卻故意說謊這種事情我最討厭了，這也是我能在業界生存那麼久的原因。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "哈哈……說起來好像也是，Vicky 姐是個直腸子的人呢。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "而且你這種不顧一切也要追到她的精神，讓我稍微想起我以前了……\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "咦？\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "沒什麼。總之現在拋開記者的身份，我很想知道你們的故事。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……我小時候……是在 Node 03 長大，跟一個叫做「Kaori」的女孩子一起……\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_04"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "허억... 허억... 비켜!\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["일반인"], "content": "우앗!\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "거기 서! NEKO! PAFF! 멈춰!\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["일반인"], "content": "NEKO랑 PAFF라고!?\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["일반인"], "content": "진짜다!\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["일반인"], "content": "빨리 찍자!\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "image", "attrs": ["nos2606"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "으아아! 망했어 망했어!\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→신호 변경]</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "아얏!\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Fall_over", "넘어진다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Vicky 누님!\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "난 신경 쓰지 말고 빨리 쫓아가!\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "어떻게 그래요!\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "제길! 하이힐을 신는 게 아니었어...\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Vicky 누님, 다리를 삔 것 같네요... 걸을 수 있겠어요?\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "문제 없... 아얏! 아파라..\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "...붓기가 곧 심해지겠는데요. 발목에 뭐라도 감싸야겠어요. 자, 제가 묶어드릴게요.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "...(손을 내민다)\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "읏차...!\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "발걸음"], "content": ""}, {"id": 22, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "......\n...어째서 계속 쫓지 않은 거야!? 쳇! 월급 까버릴 줄 알아!\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "아파파파...\n그 거리를 어떻게 쫓아가요. 중간에 사람들도 많았고.\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "너 일부러 속도 낮췄지? 걔가 계속 널 돌아봤을 때!\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "Daniel의 집에서 말했던 거... 사실이야?\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "이래 봬도 나 전문 기자야. \n단번에 알 수 있어. 넌 이미 완전히 네 개인적인 이유로 이 사건을 쫓고 있어. 분명 내게 말하지 않은 것들도 더 있겠지?\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "...정말 당해낼 수 없네요, Vicky 누님은... 죄송해요... 제가 입을 열면 이 사건은 분명 독점 뉴스로 대대적으로 보도되겠죠. 전 그렇게 되는 거 원치 않아요...\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "하아... 지금 일이 이 지경이 됐는데 독점이고 나발이고 다... 보라고. iM에 벌써 퍼지기 시작했어.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "와아...\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "이번 사건의 취재는 완전히 나의 실패야... 본래 그 사건은 완전 의외의 다른 것들과 연결되어 있는 거겠지. 네가 알고 있는 걸 내게 말해 봐.\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "안심해...\n...그 아이를 바라보던 눈빛... 지금 뭔가 위험에 처해있는 거지? 만약 뉴스 보도로 누군가의 목숨과 안전이 위험해진다면 나는 손을 땔 거니까. 아직 그 정도의 상도덕은 있다고.\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "약속하실 수 있어요...?\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "나 Vicky Russell이야! 특기는 반박, 추론, 비판, 토론! 다들 말과 관련돼있지만 그중에 거짓말은 포함돼있지 않아. 진실을 알면서도 거짓말을 하는 행위는 못 보는 사람이야. 이건 내가 이 업계에서 끝까지 살아남은 이유이기도 해.\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "하하하... 맞는 말인 것 같네요. Vicky 누님은 그래도 올곧은 사람이니까.\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "너처럼 물불 안 가리고 그 아이에게 달려가는 모습을 보니... 참 옛날 생각나게 만드네...\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "네?\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "아무것도 아니야. 어쨌든 지금 기자의 신분을 벗어나서, 네 이야기를 진심으로 들어보고 싶어.\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "...저는 어렸을 때... Node 03에서 자랐어요. 「Kaori」라고 불리는 친구와 함께...\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_04"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "哈……哈！借過！\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["路人"], "content": "哇！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "別跑！NEKO！PAFF！站住！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["路人"], "content": "那是 NEKO 跟 PAFF 嗎！？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["路人"], "content": "真的是她們！\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["路人"], "content": "快點拍呀！\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "image", "attrs": ["nos2606"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "哇哇哇！這下糟了！\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "哇！\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Fall_over", "摔倒"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Vicky 姐！\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "別管我！繼續追！\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "那怎麼行！？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "可惡！不該穿高跟鞋的……\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Vicky 姐，妳的腳扭傷了……可以走嗎？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "可以啦……唔啊！好痛……\n"}, {"id": 18,